text: Anuvis Anays Angulo Castillo (born 3 May 2001) is a Panamanian footballer who plays as a forward for the Panama women's national team. ==International career== Angulo appeared in one match for Panama at the 2018 CONCACAF Women's Championship. ==References== Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Panamanian women's footballers Category:Panama women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards
